description:
Love Beets Organic Classic Vinegar Marinated Baby Beets, 6.5 oz
Love Beets' Organic Classic Vinegar marinated baby beets are perfect for beet lovers and beet newbies alike! They're cooked, ready-to-eat, and great for a fun and flavorful addition to salads, sandwiches, or even just snacking on right out of the pack. These Organic Classic Vinegar marinated baby beets are deliciously simple with just a touch of white vinegar that complements the beets' natural sweetness! Crafted using premium ingredients, they're organic, non-GMO, gluten-free, kosher, vegan, and have no added colors or preservatives. No mess, no fuss - just delicious beets!
